Freeman&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17273822" author="ffang" created="Thu, 28 Jan 2021 16:08:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=reta&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;reta&quot;&gt;reta&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That change was introduced to resolve a TTL problem during SSL for early OpenJDK 11 version. Since I can&apos;t see this version in latest OpenJDK 11(also in OpenJDK 14), I reverted that change.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cheers&lt;br/&gt;
Freeman &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17273933" author="reta" created="Thu, 28 Jan 2021 18:44:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks a lot, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ffang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ffang&quot;&gt;ffang&lt;/a&gt; !&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17274231" author="pibakke" created="Fri, 29 Jan 2021 08:16:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ffang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ffang&quot;&gt;ffang&lt;/a&gt;&#160;and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=reta&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;reta&quot;&gt;reta&lt;/a&gt;. Looking forward to the new 3.4.3 version. A question though. Any plans to upgrade to HTTPCORE5 in the near future (as part of 3.5.0 maybe)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
